  "keyFeatures": [
    "Voxel game engine built in C++ with Lua scripting support",
    "Easy mod and game creation via the Lua API",
    "Multiplayer support with client-server architecture",
    "Procedural map generation with multiple mapgen algorithms",
    "ContentDB for community mods, games, and texture packs",
    "Cross-platform: Linux, Windows, macOS, Android",
    "Formspec UI system for building in-game interfaces",
    "Support for SQLite, LevelDB, PostgreSQL, and Redis map backends"
  ],
